					Customized care plans tailored to individual needs, preferences, and health requirements.
				</p>
			</div>

			<div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-lg shadow-md hover:shadow-lg transition-shadow">
				<div class="w-16 h-16 bg-blue-600 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mb-6">
					<svg class="w-8 h-8 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
